PATENT RIGHTS

This software implements methods described in European Patent
Applications EP26162901.8 (filed 2026-03-06) and EP26166054.2
(filed 2026-03-19), both owned by Quantamix Solutions B.V.,
Buitendijks 2, 1422 MM Uithoorn, The Netherlands.

These patents cover, among other methods:
- Multi-signal document retrieval with trust-aware scoring
- Five-pillar development governance scoring (DRACE)
- Three-layer semantic governance validation (SemanticSHACLGate)
- Four-pass streaming intelligence compilation
- Twelve-detector compile-time invariant analysis
- Four-phase adversarial debate protocol
- Cross-query activation memory with Bayesian boosting
- Dual-backend graph data science intelligence
- Scope boundary enforcement with transitive impact detection
- Tamper-evident SHA-256 hash-chain audit trails
- Privacy-preserving redaction with greedy precedence matching
- Real-time streaming reasoning orchestration

